The paper discusses software product line engineering, which is a subfield of software engineering (cs.SE). It also mentions the potential increase in software development productivity, which is related to software development (cs.SD). The paper presents a business maturity model for software product line engineering, which falls under the category of software process improvement (cs.PL) and software engineering management (cs.CE). Finally, the paper reports on case studies, which could fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) if the case studies involved the use of machine learning techniques.
